dct_description_sm: By Edwd. Weller, F.R.G.S. ; London, published by Cassell, Petter & Galpin, La Belle Sauvage Yard, Ludgate Hill, E.C.
Shows waterways, regional and tribal names, towns.
Presence of Kroonstad and Lake Albert, and absence of British presence north of Cape Hope Colony, date this map to 1865-84.
